# GSD Skill Metadata
pack_id: DOMESTIC-101
pack_name: "Home Economics & Life Skills — Foundational Knowledge Pack"
version: 1.0.0
release_date: "2026-02-20"

# Status & Classification
status: alpha
classification: specialized
learning_domain: life_skills

# Content Description
description: |
  Home economics as essential life competency: cooking nutritious meals,
  managing a household budget, basic sewing and repair, cleaning and
  organization, and the practical skills that make independent living
  possible. Not gendered or old-fashioned, but essential knowledge that
  everyone needs and few schools still teach. Covers kitchen skills,
  textiles, household management, personal finance, and self-sufficiency
  from foundation through adult level.

short_description: "Practical life skills: cooking, sewing, cleaning, budgeting, and self-sufficiency for everyone"

# Authorship & Attribution
contributors:
  - name: "GSD Foundation"
    role: architect
  - name: "Home Economics Education Working Group"
    role: content_creators

copyright: "Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 (CC-BY-SA-4.0)"
maintained_by: GSD-Foundational-Knowledge

# Dependencies & Prerequisites
dependencies: []
prerequisite_packs: []
recommended_prior_knowledge:
  - NUTR-101
  - ECON-101

# What This Pack Enables
enables: []

